/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然當中講嘅嘢有啲離地，但戰鬥畫面非常華麗，啲GN粒子噴嚟噴去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有就係舒格堡喺背後操縱一切，去到劇場版先發現所有嘢都喺佢掌握之中<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有新人蒼月昇，聲線似阿寶似到十足十<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nExia，Dynames，OO之類嘅機會都勁有獨特風格，唔似Aegis，Justice同Infinite Justice換下幾個位嘅色就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每次嘅結局大戰都好震撼，睇過就明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n入門高達一定要睇00，話睇鐵血嗰啲係fake 鳩你，睇完00就可以睇Seed Destiny<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2500393d2f48a245a80afd4226b60cbac75bf9d","tid":2456141,"uid":370062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a9c4ab1a67a72e65a18eb469be5e0bdfce13dcac","tid":2456141,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:22:43.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>佢有出色嘅人設同靚仔靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有唔同嘅勢力互相衝突<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n主角羣係主要國家外勢力而且會不時亂入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n主角羣嘅機體比其他人嘅機體勁好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺第一季最尾，除咗主角羣嘅勢力決定和解<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但喺第二季，衝突又再次展開<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有好多外傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n主角係獨一無二嘅存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n主角會成日換機體<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n主角一個打全場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一季嘅重要角色死咗之後，第二季又有一個好似樣嘅人出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇錯！佢就係高達<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n.<br />\n.<